HELLO 
Hello brodders!
I wanna give you this supermegadoopercool collab map! 
Almost 6 months of painstaking work have not gone in vain, and now I can present to you bhop_frotinity2!!!!
In my opinion, my most fun, difficult, and best project of mine. Yes, I understand that not everyone may like such a long map, but be more fun to look at it from the other side and you may understand that I did not do it because of some desire, but because of the love for this work, I called my friends with who I would nice to work together, of course not everyone answered, but it turned out more and cooler than I expected, I hope to hear from you as many nice words)
Warning this map have alot of hight qualtity models,textures and etc, so be carefull when you open this, becouse you maybe will have not 300+fps.
8 Stages - 6 mappers 
4-5 tier
4-6 Mins long
Awesome to look 
Hope you enjoy it)
If you find some bug or my mistake or problem on the map write me there in a comments, ty!!!
